sh reality leave <br>Leaving me with the memory of our friendship which will last forever<br>My only wish is to spread the light of acceptance and understanding into the dark world, so that they may return <br>I am Zarath, a wandering minstral in search of his friends.<br>-In memory of Sarian, Sidewinders and Genosem, may we meet again.</td></td></tr><tr><td colspan="2" class="mform2"><table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" width="100%"><tr><td id="fs8">Posting from Canada</td></tr></table>
